data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the charming neighborhood of Annaville, just a short 20-minute drive away from the bustling city of Corpus Christi. This 4-bedroom, 2 full bath brick home offers a blend of comfort, and convenience. As you step inside, you are greeted by a spacious and inviting living area adorned with natural light flowing through large windows. The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, creating an ideal space for entertaining guests and spending quality time with loved ones. With everything this home has to offer, its ready to welcome any homeowner to start their new chapter! This property has so much potential to create your own design and call it home! Call today to get all the details and schedule a private tour!
